#: ../../source/vuln/middleware/iis.rst:2
msgid "IIS"
msgstr "IIS"

#: ../../source/vuln/middleware/iis.rst:5
msgid "IIS 6.0"
msgstr "IIS 6.0"

#: ../../source/vuln/middleware/iis.rst:6
msgid "后缀解析 ``/xx.asp;.jpg``"
msgstr "Extension parsing: ``/xx.asp;.jpg``"

#: ../../source/vuln/middleware/iis.rst:7
msgid "服务器默认不解析 ``;`` 号及其后面的内容，相当于截断。"
msgstr ""
"By default, the server does not parse ``;`` or anything after it, which is "
"equivalent to truncation."

#: ../../source/vuln/middleware/iis.rst:8
msgid "目录解析 ``/xx.asp/xx.jpg`` (xx.asp目录下任意解析)"
msgstr ""
"Directory parsing: ``/xx.asp/xx.jpg``; arbitrary parsing under the "
"``xx.asp`` directory"

#: ../../source/vuln/middleware/iis.rst:9
msgid "默认解析 ``xx.asa`` ``xx.cer`` ``xx.cdx``"
msgstr "Parses ``xx.asa`` ``xx.cer`` ``xx.cdx`` by default"

#: ../../source/vuln/middleware/iis.rst:10
msgid "PROPFIND 栈溢出漏洞"
msgstr "PROPFIND stack overflow vulnerability"

#: ../../source/vuln/middleware/iis.rst:11
msgid "RCE CVE-2017-7269"
msgstr "RCE CVE-2017-7269"

#: ../../source/vuln/middleware/iis.rst:14
msgid "IIS 7.0-7.5 / Nginx <= 0.8.37"
msgstr "IIS 7.0-7.5 / Nginx <= 0.8.37"

#: ../../source/vuln/middleware/iis.rst:15
msgid "在Fast-CGI开启状态下，在文件路径后加上 ``/xx.php`` ，即 ``xx.jpg/xx.php`` 会被解析为php文件。"
msgstr ""
"When Fast-CGI is enabled, appending ``/xx.php`` to a file path, such as "
"``xx.jpg/xx.php``, causes it to be parsed as a PHP file."

#: ../../source/vuln/middleware/iis.rst:18
msgid "PUT漏洞"
msgstr "PUT Vulnerability"

#: ../../source/vuln/middleware/iis.rst:19
msgid "开启WebDAV"
msgstr "WebDAV is enabled"

#: ../../source/vuln/middleware/iis.rst:20
msgid "拥有来宾用户，且来宾用户拥有上传权限"
msgstr "A guest user exists and has upload permissions"

#: ../../source/vuln/middleware/iis.rst:21
msgid "可任意文件上传"
msgstr "Arbitrary file upload is possible"

#: ../../source/vuln/middleware/iis.rst:24
msgid "Windows特性"
msgstr "Windows Behavior"

#: ../../source/vuln/middleware/iis.rst:25
msgid ""
"Windows不允许空格和点以及一些特殊字符作为结尾，创建这样的文件会自动重命名，所以可以使用 ``xx.php[空格]`` ， "
"``xx.php.``， ``xx.php/``， ``xx.php::$DATA`` 上传脚本文件。"
msgstr ""
"Windows does not allow spaces, dots, or some special characters at the end "
"of filenames, and automatically renames such files when they are created. "
"Therefore, ``xx.php[space]``, ``xx.php.``, ``xx.php/``, and "
"``xx.php::$DATA`` can be used to upload script files."

#: ../../source/vuln/middleware/iis.rst:28
msgid "文件名猜解"
msgstr "Filename Guessing"

#: ../../source/vuln/middleware/iis.rst:29
msgid "在支持NTFS 8.3文件格式时，可利用短文件名猜解目录文件。其中短文件名特征如下："
msgstr ""
"When NTFS 8.3 filenames are supported, short filenames can be used to guess "
"directory files. Short filenames have the following characteristics:"

#: ../../source/vuln/middleware/iis.rst:31
msgid "文件名为原文件名前6位字符加上 ``~1`` ，其中数字部分是递增的，如果存在前缀相同的文件，则后面的数字进行递增。"
msgstr ""
"The filename consists of the first six characters of the original filename "
"plus ``~1``. The numeric part increments; if files with the same prefix "
"exist, the later number increments."

#: ../../source/vuln/middleware/iis.rst:32
msgid "后缀名不超过3位，超过部分会被截断"
msgstr "The extension is at most three characters; any extra part is truncated."

#: ../../source/vuln/middleware/iis.rst:33
msgid "所有小写字母均转换成大写的字母"
msgstr "All lowercase letters are converted to uppercase."

#: ../../source/vuln/middleware/iis.rst:34
msgid "文件名后缀长度大于等于4或者总长度大于等于9时才会生成短文件名，如果包含空格或者其他部分特殊字符，则无视长度条件"
msgstr ""
"Short filenames are generated only when the extension length is at least 4 "
"or the total length is at least 9. If the name contains spaces or some other"
" special characters, the length condition is ignored."

#: ../../source/vuln/middleware/iis.rst:36
msgid ""
"IIS "
"8.0之前的版本支持短文件名猜测的HTTP方法主要包括：DEBUG、OPTIONS、GET、POST、HEAD、TRACE六种，需要安装ASP.NET。而IIS"
" 8.0之后的版本只能通过OPTIONS和TRACE方法猜测成功，但是没有ASP.NET的限制。"
msgstr ""
"Before IIS 8.0, HTTP methods that support short filename guessing mainly "
"include DEBUG, OPTIONS, GET, POST, HEAD, and TRACE, and ASP.NET must be "
"installed. After IIS 8.0, guessing succeeds only through OPTIONS and TRACE, "
"but there is no ASP.NET requirement."

#: ../../source/vuln/middleware/iis.rst:38
msgid "这种方法的局限性在于："
msgstr "The limitations of this method are:"

#: ../../source/vuln/middleware/iis.rst:40
msgid "文件夹名前6位字符带点”.”，扫描程序会认为是文件而不是文件夹，最终出现误报"
msgstr ""
"If the first six characters of a folder name contain a dot ``.``, scanners "
"may treat it as a file rather than a folder, causing false positives."

#: ../../source/vuln/middleware/iis.rst:41
msgid "不支持中文文件名"
msgstr "Chinese filenames are not supported"

#: ../../source/vuln/middleware/iis.rst:43
msgid "这种方法可以通过命令 ``fsutil behavior set disable8dot3 1`` 关闭NTFS 8.3文件格式的支持来修复。"
msgstr ""
"This can be fixed by disabling NTFS 8.3 filename support with ``fsutil "
"behavior set disable8dot3 1``."

